  : 2. Lifetime '*static' must outlive '*stack'
  .
 ... caused by 1.
  -> 'SomeStruct*static' assigned to pointer with lifetime '*stack'
  :
 == note: pointee 'SomeStruct' is lifetime-strict cannot have its lifetime shortened.
 == help: try using a const pointer to make this lifetime-permissive.
